data.description: BUYERS CREDIT TOWARDS CLOSING IF CLOSED PRIOR TO 12/28/23.  You will love this newly updated home in the heart of Cleveland! New paint inside and out, hardwood flooring(walnut stain), new lighting and fans, new kitchen flooring, cabinets, countertops, sink and fixtures, new stainless stove and microwave oven.  Oversized bedrooms with lots of closet space. New front, back and storage room insulated doors.  New landscaping with numerous cedar trees planted for privacy. Oversized corner lot provides a private storm shelter, 2 story playhouse, storage building, and your very own planter boxes out back for a herb garden - all nestled on a flat corner lot.  Attached carport has storage room large enough for an additional fridge or freezer.
